{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dcd77aa397","title":"力求消灭敌一部","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a4156da569","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":8,"articleId":"dcd77aa397"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"608b1c6043","type":"paragraph","text":"力求消灭敌一部","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"dcd77aa397"},{"id":"6f6c364216","type":"paragraph","text":"1936年11月8日）彭，并转张、朱，贺、任","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"dcd77aa397"},{"id":"bc6c4f3616","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、现在地区力求消灭敌一部，就是一、二个团也好。给此打击的作用有二：第一调动胡以部第一师增加到宁夏，以利尔后机动；第二使敌进得慢些，我在金灵才有余裕时间筹粮休息。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"dcd77aa397"},{"id":"c39e72b034","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、打法仍以待其前进为妙，惟不必待周孔两师问，打一个师亦好。望豹。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"dcd77aa397"},{"id":"f3127c0d99","type":"paragraph","text":"毛周","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"dcd77aa397"},{"id":"d30d700b43","type":"paragraph","text":"八号二十时","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"dcd77aa397"},{"id":"669187be50","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东和周恩来给红军前敌总指挥兼政治委员、第一方面军司今员彭德怀的电报。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"dcd77aa397"},{"id":"d698aa9131","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]张，指张国意，当时任红军总政治委员。朱，指朱德。贺、任，指贺龙、任强时，当时分别任红军第二方面军总指挥和政治委员。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"dcd77aa397"},{"id":"44645622e6","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]胡，指胡宗南，当时任国民党军西北“剩”总司令部第一路第二纵队（第一军）司令兼第一师师长。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"dcd77aa397"},{"id":"c33e16591c","type":"paragraph","text":"[4]金，指金积，旧县名，1960年撤销，辖区裁入宁夏吴忠、青铜峡二市。灵，指宁夏灵武。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"dcd77aa397"},{"id":"81a55c302f","type":"paragraph","text":"[5]周孔两师，指国民党军西北“汇”总司令部第一路第二纵队第四十三师和第九十七师，师长分别为周祥初和孔令愉。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"dcd77aa397"}],"page":{"id":"72b0715ba6","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"dcd77aa397","start":280,"end":280}}}},"__N_SSG":true}